# Normal pipeline
./01.findchirps 
./02.trim
./03-e.multitile.py
./04.manual-crop.py < manual

# Pipeline wishlist
./01.findchirps
./02.trim_and_glue_and_freeze (automatically freezes to the length of master wav -- skip last 0.5 seconds of video)
./05.make_caption < with gridspec
./04-e.multitile < with grid spec on each video (including caption video)
./05.manual_crop.py < crop and final touches

# Looping pipeline
./01.findchirps
./02.trim_and_glue (NOT freeze frame)
./03.loop_only_audio < loop spec (includes bar structure)
./04.loop_audio_and_video < loop spec
./05.multitile < grid spec
This doesnt need manual cropping because we already have the bar structure in loop spec
